name: Level Warp
description:
Level Warp, Is a platformer were you will be able to control the levels to complete the stages, You can collect Coins/Gems as you go through stages, This the game that i made for my Game Jam(Mini Jam 101).

Controls

-> WASD to move level

-> Space to move player

-> Purple Bar will make you go in the opposite direction

->Yellow Bar will make your player jump
